{"id":831401,"date":[{"year":1991,"month":1,"day":14}],"page":"2","source":"","region":"","masthead":"综合新闻","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"246","ytitle":"","mtitle":"仙人掌","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"上海普陀区泰山新村小学，虹口区崇明路小学及黄浦区少年宫日前在黄浦区图书馆幽默博览室举办了一个少儿漫画展。不少小朋友用漫画形式反映了自己身边的生活，从笑声中使自己分清是与非，明白美与丑，进行自我道德教育。我们从这个展览中选刊了部分作品，希望有更多的小小漫画家在精神文明建设中健康成长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入9号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1991\\01\\911e020701.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>叶蕾</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>玩不起来　叶蕾(9岁)</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入9号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1991\\01\\911e020702.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>朱义莹</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>“长锋”(幽默画)朱义莹(8岁)</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入9号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1991\\01\\911e020703.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>毛旭丹</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>简易绷带(幽默画)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛旭丹(11岁)</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入9号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1991\\01\\911e020704.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>周欣人</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>叶叶皆辛苦　周欣人(10岁)</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入9号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1991\\01\\911e020705.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>王振义</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>看电视　王振义(9岁)</FONT>"}]}